Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.93,0:01:54.31,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}Now let me open the scar
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.39,0:01:56.85,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}溶け合ったVirus
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.60,0:02:06.07,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}虹に黒を差し飛び立つ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.04,0:02:21.29,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}赤い花の蜜 濡れて隠れたノイズ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.50,0:02:30.05,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}胸に這い寄るの　ウマレカワリタイノデショウ?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.14,0:02:34.72,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}永遠 眠っていたパラダイム
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.89,0:02:40.94,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}芯を喰って侵食していた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.94,0:02:44.28,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}Now let me open the scar
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.48,0:02:46.82,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}溶け合ったVirus
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.86,0:02:51.49,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}触れて露わになる本能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.66,0:02:53.99,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}Grew up in the loneliness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.16,0:02:56.50,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}壊れたReality
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.33,0:03:05.80,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}虹に黒を差し飛び立つ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.92,0:03:09.88,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}今すぐ抜け出して 正気の迷路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.01,0:03:11.59,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}反転したコントラストへ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.93,0:01:54.31,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}现在让我来揭开伤疤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.39,0:01:56.85,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}再把病毒融入进去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.60,0:02:06.07,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}划破苍穹  将虹桥染上漆黑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.04,0:02:21.29,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}血色花蜜将匿藏的杂音暴露在外
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.50,0:02:30.05,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}寄居在心房的某个声音  诱述着是否想死亡轮回?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.14,0:02:34.72,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}那是一直沉眠的睡美人的楷模
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.89,0:02:40.94,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}侵蚀将从心脏开始  然后蔓延全身
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.94,0:02:44.28,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}现在让我来揭开伤疤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.48,0:02:46.82,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}再把病毒融入进去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.86,0:02:51.49,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}隐藏本能的外壳  几乎一碰就碎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.66,0:02:53.99,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}于孤独中成长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.16,0:02:56.50,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}还有残破的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.33,0:03:05.80,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}划破苍穹  将虹桥染上漆黑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.92,0:03:09.88,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}现在马上冲出这个疯狂的迷宫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.01,0:03:11.59,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}将情况逆转吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Comment,,0,0,0,,——ED——
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.62,0:24:48.03,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The ticket is all that I have lost
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.04,0:24:51.91,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}十分な喪失と招待され
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.08,0:24:54.62,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Today's program is a tragedy
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.46,0:24:58.59,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}救済の一切もない名作を
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.71,0:25:04.84,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Please be quiet. Hope is noisy
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.47,0:25:08.05,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The dreams rot off and drop away
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.68,0:25:11.77,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}望みこそ腐敗の元凶
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.81,0:25:14.69,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}No wish, no smile, only despair
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.69,0:25:18.52,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The curtain will open
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.77,0:25:21.57,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Welcome to the party
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.69,0:25:25.28,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}暗闇で舞う無数の影よ
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.45,0:25:28.20,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}This show will never end
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.37,0:25:35.21,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}何人も逃れられはしない
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.62,0:24:48.03,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这张票是我已失去的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.04,0:24:51.91,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那是让人失去一切的招待
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.08,0:24:54.62,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}今天在上演的是一出悲剧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.46,0:24:58.59,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那是毫无救济的名作
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.71,0:25:04.84,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}希望过于嘈杂  请安静
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.47,0:25:08.05,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那些幻梦早已消失殆尽
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.68,0:25:11.77,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}希望正是腐败的元凶
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.81,0:25:14.69,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}禁止许愿  禁止欢笑  只有绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.69,0:25:18.52,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}大幕将要拉开
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.77,0:25:21.57,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}欢迎来到这个派对
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.69,0:25:25.28,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}在漆黑中起舞的众多黑影
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.45,0:25:28.20,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这出戏将永不落幕
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.37,0:25:35.21,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}没有人能从中脱身解救
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Comment,,0,0,0,,——Title——
